47
00:03:52,326 --> 00:03:56,998
That I would protect Yeong-ro.

48
00:03:58,541 --> 00:03:59,667
<i>Mom.</i>

49
00:04:01,627 --> 00:04:03,421
I'll protect Yeong-ro.

50
00:04:04,380 --> 00:04:05,673
So don't worry.

51
00:04:06,674 --> 00:04:08,718
I'll make sure she marries

52
00:04:08,801 --> 00:04:10,970
someone who loves her so much.

53
00:04:11,846 --> 00:04:15,808
And I'll look out for her by her side
until she becomes an old lady,

54
00:04:16,392 --> 00:04:18,102
so don't worry about a thing, Mom.

55
00:04:19,270 --> 00:04:21,314
I'm just three years younger than you.

56
00:04:30,614 --> 00:04:31,490
Dad.

57
00:04:32,408 --> 00:04:33,492
Yes?

58
00:04:35,786 --> 00:04:37,204
