59
00:04:43,878 --> 00:04:45,421
Keep her safe.

60
00:04:46,505 --> 00:04:47,923
Of course, I will.

61
00:04:48,507 --> 00:04:51,427
But you should get better
and do it yourself.

62
00:04:53,429 --> 00:04:54,764
You should do that.

63
