on the West Sea around 22:00 last night,</i>

82
00:08:46,453 --> 00:08:50,332
<i>Eun Yeong-u, the son of the ANSP director,
was injured and passed away.</i>

83
00:08:50,416 --> 00:08:54,378
<i>It has been known that the person KIA
was corporate Kim Seong-hun,</i>

84
00:08:54,461 --> 00:08:57,631
<i>but it turned out
that it was marine Eun Yeong-u,</i>

85
00:08:57,715 --> 00:08:59,842
<i>the ANSP director's son, that died.</i>

86
00:08:59,925 --> 00:09:02,011
<i>What's more shocking is that Lim Soo-ho,</i>

87
00:09:02,094 --> 00:09:04,805
<i>the leader of the spies
who killed Eun Yeong-u,</i>

88
00:09:04,888 --> 00:09:08,809
<i>is holding the students hostage
in Hosu University dorm as we speak.</i>

89
00:09:08,892 --> 00:09:12,313
<i>He'd been acting secretly
all over East Germany,</i>

90
00:09:12,396 --> 00:09:15,691
<i>but he disguised himself as an economics
graduate student at Berlin University</i>

91
00:09:15,774 --> 00:09:17,610
<i>and came to Korea</i>

92
00:09:17,693 --> 00:09:20,362
<i>to approach Professor Han I-seop.</i>

93
00:09:20,654 --> 00:09:24,241
<i>This is the shocking truth revealed a day
after the engagement on the West Sea.</i>

94
00:09:24,325 --> 00:09:27,244
<i>We will update you
as soon as we find out more.</i>

95
00:09:47,431 --> 00:09:48,432
What…

96
00:09:49,683 --> 00:09:51,185
What did she just say?

97
00:09:56,106 --> 00:09:57,399
My brother…

98
00:09:59,860 --> 00:10:01,195
was killed?

99
00:10:12,790 --> 00:10:15,250
My brother is dead?

100
00:10:25,469 --> 00:10:26,470
No…

101
00:10:29,973 --> 00:10:31,100
No…

102
00:10:31,767 --> 00:10:32,810
No…

103
00:10:33,727 --> 00:10:35,479
It can't be true.

104
00:10:37,272 --> 00:10:39,942
Why… Why is my brother dead?

105
00:10:40,025 --> 00:10:40,984
No…

106
00:10:42,486 --> 00:10:43,737
That's not true…

107
00:10:48,367 --> 00:10:50,953
Yeong-u… Yeong-u!

108
00:10:55,124 --> 00:10:57,126
Yeong-u… Yeong-u!

109
00:10:57,209 --> 00:10:58,127
Eun Yeong-ro!

110
00:10:59,294 --> 00:11:00,129
Eun Yeong-ro!

111
00:11:03,340 --> 00:11:04,508
-Yeong-ro!
-Yeong-u!

112
00:11:06,385 --> 00:11:09,388
Let go! Let go of me!

113
00:11:09,972 --> 00:11:11,056
Calm down!

114
00:11:12,850 --> 00:11:14,768
I need to go see for myself!

115
00:11:18,355 --> 00:11:20,482
It's dangerous.
You don't want to die, do you?

116
00:11:48,677 --> 00:11:50,637
You're the leader of those
who killed Yeong-u?

117
00:11:51,805 --> 00:11:53,557
You evil bastard.

118
00:11:53,640 --> 00:11:56,435
Holding us hostage wasn't enough?
Why did you kill my brother?

119
00:11:56,518 --> 00:11:58,187
What did he do wrong?

120
00:11:58,270 --> 00:12:00,481
He didn't do anything to deserve it!

121
00:12:03,066 --> 00:12:04,401
Bring him back.

122
00:12:05,110 --> 00:12:06,904
Bring him back!

